This is a rudimentary begin of a test suite for NHW images

* analysis.py  : Python script to get a more detailed info about image
                 differences
* Makefile     : Rules to batch-create and -compare images


analysis.py
============

Usage:  python analysis.py image1.nhw image2.nhw

Makefile
=========

Quick notes:

* Source PNG files are in $(TESTDIR)
* Output NHWs are in $(WORKDIR)
* Reference ('golden') images in $(REFDIR)


Examples:

Encode all PNGs im $(TESTDIR) to NHWs:

> make clean all-nhw

Do a full PNG loopback on all test images:

> make clean all

Copy generated NHWs into reference directory:

> make reference

Compare a specific testimage specified by $(TESTIMAGE) to reference:

> make testdiff TESTIMAGE=my_image_without_extension

View test image differences in detail:

> make diff TESTIMAGE=my_image_without_extension

